data: Before we begin, please enter a valid Sacramento State email
Invalid email, must be a CSUS email
Password must be at least 8 characters long, have one uppercase letter, one lowercase letter, and one number
These can be identified by the “@csus.edu” handle near the end like this:
Next, please create a suitable password for your new account.
For security purposes, please make sure that your password contains a series of numbers, letters, and other special characters.
DON'T share your password with other users or third-parties. It should only be known by the owner of the account
Almost there! Please confirm the password you just created by entering it one more time.
Finally, add an image that you want to use to represent yourself
Please be mindful of other users, Avoid using images that may be considered disturbing or offensive. Images should be inline with Sac State's Hornet Honor Code policy
